Just make cool and catchy design. What I want to see on the page (only this, nothing else, no other elements):
- Header: You Grow the Business. Our AI Grows the Brand.
- Subheader: Our AI analyzes your Facebook history to master your unique brand voice, then posts for you automatically—exactly as often as you choose
- Button: Get Started
- Gif: use gif ![from path gif/gif-blue.gif](gif/gif-blue.gif)

Steps to implement one by one regarding to landing page:
- Create header and subheader at the top. 
Requirements: Subheader should be italic. Highligt 'Our AI analyzes your Facebook history' and 'posts for you automatically' in some cool style which will attract attention
- Add button "Get Started" at the middle of the page
Requirements: Button should be well designed according to general style of landing page, should DO NO action
- Add GIF element
Requirements: GIF is fixed to the bottom of the screen, horizontally centered, and spans almost the full viewport width. Initially, half of it is hidden below the viewport edge. On hover, it animates upward and bicame smallet, Subheader should be hidden, button should be a little bit bigger and go a little but up together with header, GIF should NEVER cover Button and Header. The image itself is cropped using clip-path inset to remove outer edges (more from top, less from bottom, symmetrical on sides) with subtle rounded corners. The wrapper has pointer cursor and sits below the CTA button in z-index stacking.

